{"tid":1864383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"武肺社區爆發由銅鑼灣Apple Store開始","createTime":"2020-02-05T14:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T02:15:31.000Z","uid":333791,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b1afc735d7083355e4efd080cb7391d97d78815b","tid":1864383,"uid":333791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"代朋友po的：<br />\n<br />\n今日銅鑼灣Apple Store派假口罩比同事，屌。冇口罩就咪撚派，啲同事點都會自備。<br />\n<br />\n好過用啲假野厄人啲同事知又唔知，個個戴撚左啲假野。<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣舖有幾百個Retail同事，係幾百！日日又對住啲大陸西客，幾百人有一個奶野，真係全部都攬炒。<br />\n<br />\n佢地有屋企人有朋友，一個傳一個，全港社區爆發由銅鑼灣Apple Store做起。各位手足千祈唔好去Apple！高危地帶！"},{"pid":"ea895f7e70cd66a35bedcae2b3214f0750cfa37d","tid":1864383,"uid":333791,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vtuGyRz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvtuGyRz.jpg&h=15acea4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tP3NbA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tP3NbA.jpg&h=83082c5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a53350dc10cdb795aa34a71656eff2a0d5e5f1a","tid":1864383,"uid":333791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:46:58.000Z","msg":"自推10次 1/10"},{"pid":"60a69747908b98875cde8cc7658e299f335adc2b","tid":1864383,"uid":333791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:47:14.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"d71ff18d9dcd34706da754ff83e53b3c8fd25bb1","tid":1864383,"uid":333791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:47:29.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"5bd2cc0f948ea2a9e82131db4df1cb5cd41160b5","tid":1864383,"uid":333791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:47:44.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"ea5a1c3452fb4ae8dd4e32d43b5631c9813e5a31","tid":1864383,"uid":333791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:47:56.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"dd21ce39e942a54250